Package: curvedns
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends},
Architecture: any
Description: DNS/DNSCurve forwarding name server - binaries
 The curvedns package provides software for DNS/DNSCurve.
 .
 CurveDNS is the first publicly released forwarding implementation
 that implements the DNSCurve protocol

Package: curvedns-run
Depends: adduser,
         daemontools-run,
         curvedns,
         ${misc:Depends},
Architecture: all
Description: DNS/DNSCurve forwarding name server - running under daemontools
 The curvedns package provides software for DNS/DNSCurve.
 .
 curvedns-run automatically sets up the curvedns package to provide a
 curvedns service.
